<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" class="dark scroll-smooth">
<head>
   <meta charset="UTF-8">
   <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
   <title>2horas.online | Tu Web en 2 Horas</title>
   <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
   
   <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
   <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
   <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
   <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  
   <script id="tailwind-config">
       tailwind.config = {
           darkMode: "class",
           theme: {
               extend: {
                   colors: {
                       "surface": "#05050A",
                       "surface-container-lowest": "#0A0B14",
                       "surface-container-low": "#0F121F",
                       "surface-container": "#15192B",
                       "surface-container-high": "#1E233B",
                       "surface-container-highest": "#282E4D",
                       "surface-bright": "#15192B",
                       "on-surface": "#FFFFFF",
                       "on-surface-variant": "#94A3B8",
                       
                       "primary": "#0057FF",
                       "on-primary": "#FFFFFF",
                       "primary-container": "#003BCC",
                       "on-primary-container": "#E0E7FF",
                       "primary-fixed": "#00F0FF",
                       "on-primary-fixed-variant": "#003BCC",
                       
                       "secondary": "#00F0FF",
                       "on-secondary": "#000000",
                       "secondary-container": "#008A99",
                       
                       "outline": "#475569",
                       "outline-variant": "#1E233B",
                       
                       "error": "#FF2E54",
                       "error-container": "#4C0519",
                   },
                   fontFamily: {
                       "headline": ["'Space Grotesk'", "sans-serif"],
                       "body": ["Inter", "sans-serif"],
                       "label": ["Inter", "sans-serif"]
                   },
                   borderRadius: {"DEFAULT": "0.25rem", "lg": "0.5rem", "xl": "0.75rem", "2xl": "1rem", "3xl": "1.5rem", "full": "9999px"},
                   animation: {
                       'float': 'float 6s ease-in-out infinite',
                       'glow': 'glow 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate',
                   },
                   keyframes: {
                       float: {
                           '0%, 100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)' },
                           '50%': { transform: 'translateY(-15px)' },
                       },
                       glow: {
                           '0%': { opacity: '0.4', filter: 'blur(60px)' },
                           '100%': { opacity: '0.8', filter: 'blur(90px)' },
                       }
                   }
               },
           },
       }
   </script>
   <style>
       .material-symbols-outlined { font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1, 'wght' 300, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24; }
       body {
           background-image: radial-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
           background-size: 30px 30px;
       }
       .glass-card {
           background: rgba(15, 18, 31, 0.7);
           backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
           -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
           border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
       }
       .step-hidden { display: none; }
       .fade-in { animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-in-out; }
       @keyframes fadeIn {
           from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
           to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
       }
       .radio-card:checked + div {
           border-color: #00F0FF; 
           background-color: rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.05);
           box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 240, 255, 0.15);
           transform: translateY(-2px);
       }
       .radio-card:checked + div span.material-symbols-outlined {
           color: #00F0FF;
           text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,240,255,0.5);
       }
       .radio-card-reject:checked + div {
           border-color: #FF2E54;
           background-color: rgba(255, 46, 84, 0.05);
           box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 46, 84, 0.15);
           transform: translateY(-2px);
       }
       ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; }
       ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #0A0B14; } 
       ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #282E4D; border-radius: 4px; } 
       ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #0057FF; } 
   </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-surface font-body text-on-surface selection:bg-secondary selection:text-on-secondary antialiased">

   <!-- Toast Notification -->
   <div id="toast" class="fixed top-24 right-4 md:right-8 z-[200] transform transition-all duration-300 translate-x-[150%] opacity-0 bg-error-container border border-error/50 text-white px-6 py-4 rounded-xl shadow-2xl flex items-center gap-3">
       <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-error">error</span>
       <span id="toastMessage" class="font-body text-sm font-medium"></span>
   </div>

   <!-- TopNavBar -->
   <nav class="bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-xl sticky top-0 z-50 border-b border-surface-container-highest">
       <div class="flex justify-between items-center w-full px-8 py-4 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
           <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
               <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-secondary rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,240,255,0.3)]">
                   <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white text-xl">bolt</span>
               </div>
               <div class="text-2xl font-black text-on-surface tracking-tighter font-headline">
                   2horas<span class="text-secondary">.online</span>
               </div>
           </div>
           <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8">
               <a class="text-on-surface font-bold border-b-2 border-secondary font-headline tracking-tight" href="#como-funciona">El Proceso</a>
               <a class="text-on-surface-variant hover:text-secondary transition-colors font-headline font-bold tracking-tight" href="#aplicar">Viabilidad</a>
           </div>
           <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
               <a href="#aplicar" class="bg-surface-container text-on-surface px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-bold text-sm font-headline border border-white/10 hover:border-secondary/50 hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all">
                   Agendar Sesión
               </a>
           </div>
       </div>
   </nav>

   <!-- Hero Section -->
   <section class="relative pt-24 pb-32 px-8 overflow-hidden">
       <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          
           <!-- Glowing Orbs -->
           <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-primary/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none animate-glow"></div>
           <div class="absolute bottom-20 right-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-secondary/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none animate-glow" style="animation-delay: 1.5s;"></div>

           <!-- Left Content -->
           <div class="z-10 flex flex-col items-start text-left">
               <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-surface-container text-secondary font-bold text-xs mb-6 border border-secondary/20 tracking-wider">
                   <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
                       <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-secondary opacity-75"></span>
                       <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-secondary"></span>
                   </span>
                   AGENCIA CaaS ASISTIDA POR IA
               </div>
              
               <h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-on-surface leading-[1.1] tracking-tighter mb-8">
                   Entras con una idea.<br>
                   <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary">Sales en 2 horas con tu web lista.</span>
               </h1>
              
               <p class="font-body text-lg md:text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed">
                   Una videollamada intensiva. Diseño profesional, arquitectura de conversión, copywriting por IA y publicada en vivo. Sin semanas de espera ni revisiones infinitas.
               </p>
              
               <!-- BOTONES -->
               <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 w-full sm:w-auto">
                   <button onclick="openModal('qualifyModal')" class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg font-headline shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,87,255,0.4)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(0,240,255,0.5)] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full sm:w-auto">
                       Verificar si califico
                       <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">rule</span>
                   </button>
                   <button onclick="openModal('howItWorksModal')" class="bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg font-headline border border-white/5 hover:bg-surface-container-highest hover:border-white/10 transition-colors flex items-center justify-center w-full sm:w-auto">
                       Ver cómo funciona
                   </button>
               </div>
           </div>

           <!-- Right Content (Hero Image) -->
           <div class="relative z-10 w-full h-[400px] lg:h-[600px] rounded-[2.5rem] p-4 lg:p-6 bg-surface-container/50 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 animate-float">
               <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary/10 to-secondary/10 rounded-[2.5rem] transform rotate-2 scale-[1.02] -z-10"></div>
               <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559097280-ce4b032b67a6?q=80&w=1470&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-[2rem] shadow-2xl grayscale-[30%] brightness-75 contrast-125">
              
               <!-- Floating glass badge -->
               <div class="absolute -left-6 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 glass-card p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl max-w-[200px] hidden md:block">
                   <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                       <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-surface-container-highest flex items-center justify-center">
                           <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-sm">bolt</span>
                       </div>
                       <div class="h-2 w-16 bg-outline-variant rounded-full"></div>
                   </div>
                   <div class="space-y-2">
                       <div class="h-1.5 w-full bg-surface-container-highest rounded-full"></div>
                       <div class="h-1.5 w-3/4 bg-surface-container-highest rounded-full"></div>
                   </div>
               </div>
           </div>
       </div>
   </section>

   <!-- How it works (The Flow) -->
   <section id="como-funciona" class="py-24 px-8 bg-surface-container-lowest border-y border-surface-container-highest relative">
       <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
           <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
               <!-- Process Image -->
               <div class="relative w-full h-[500px] lg:h-[700px] rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl order-2 lg:order-1 border border-surface-container-highest">
                   <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522086605197-deac1ce7566c?q=80&w=715&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-70 grayscale-[50%] hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700">
                   <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
                  
                   <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 right-8 glass-card p-6 rounded-2xl">
                       <p class="font-headline font-bold text-on-surface text-xl">Ejecución en vivo</p>
                       <p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant text-sm mt-1">Sin correos de ida y vuelta ni fricciones. Construimos juntos.</p>
                   </div>
               </div>

               <!-- Process Steps -->
               <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
                   <div class="mb-12">
                       <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4 text-on-surface">La arquitectura en 3 pasos</h2>
                       <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body text-lg">Un proceso productizado y estandarizado para garantizar resultados premium en tiempo récord, usando inteligencia artificial.</p>
                   </div>

                   <div class="space-y-6 relative">
                       <div class="absolute left-8 top-10 bottom-10 w-0.5 bg-outline-variant z-0 hidden md:block"></div>

                       <!-- Step 1 -->
                       <div class="relative z-10 bg-surface-container p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-white/5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 group hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-secondary/30 transition-all shadow-lg">
                           <div class="w-16 h-16 shrink-0 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-highest flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
                               <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant text-3xl group-hover:text-secondary">filter_alt</span>
                           </div>
                           <div>
                               <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-on-surface">1. Filtro & Pre-Work</h3>
                               <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">Llenas nuestra solicitud. Si es viable, usamos Claude 3.5 para generar la estructura persuasiva antes de nuestra sesión.</p>
                           </div>
                       </div>

                       <!-- Step 2 -->
                       <div class="relative z-10 bg-surface-container p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-white/5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 group hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-secondary/30 transition-all shadow-lg">
                           <div class="w-16 h-16 shrink-0 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-highest flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
                               <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant text-3xl group-hover:text-secondary">schedule</span>
                           </div>
                           <div>
                               <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-on-surface">2. Sesión Intensiva</h3>
                               <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">Videollamada de 2 horas. Aprobamos textos, aplicamos tu marca, utilizamos herramientas No-Code de alta gama y montamos en vivo.</p>
                           </div>
                       </div>

                       <!-- Step 3 -->
                       <div class="relative z-10 bg-surface-container p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-white/5 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 group hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-secondary/30 transition-all shadow-lg">
                           <div class="w-16 h-16 shrink-0 rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-highest flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary/20 transition-colors">
                               <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-surface-variant text-3xl group-hover:text-secondary">rocket_launch</span>
                           </div>
                           <div>
                               <h3 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-on-surface">3. Lanzamiento</h3>
                               <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed font-body">En los últimos 20 minutos conectamos el dominio, probamos integraciones, publicamos y te entregamos las llaves del sitio.</p>
                           </div>
                       </div>
                   </div>
               </div>
           </div>
       </div>
   </section>

   <!-- The Filter (Form Section) -->
   <section id="aplicar" class="py-24 px-8 bg-surface relative">
       <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full max-w-4xl h-[600px] bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-[150px] pointer-events-none"></div>
       
       <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start relative z-10">
          
           <!-- Left Side: Text and Form Image -->
           <div class="lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col h-full lg:sticky lg:top-28">
               <div class="mb-8">
                   <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4 text-on-surface">Solicitud de Viabilidad</h2>
                   <p class="text-on-surface-variant font-body text-lg">Para garantizar nuestra promesa de 2 horas, tu proyecto debe cumplir parámetros específicos. Evaluemos tu caso.</p>
               </div>
              
               <div class="relative rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden flex-grow min-h-[400px] shadow-2xl border border-white/10 hidden lg:block">
                   <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1461749280684-dccba630e2f6?q=80&w=1469&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[40%] brightness-50">
                   <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-primary/30 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
                   <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface via-surface/50 to-transparent"></div>
               </div>
           </div>

           <!-- Right Side: Form -->
           <div class="lg:col-span-7 bg-surface-container/80 backdrop-blur-xl rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] border border-white/10 overflow-hidden relative">
              
               <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-secondary/10 rounded-bl-[100px] pointer-events-none blur-xl"></div>

               <div class="p-8 md:p-12">
                   <form id="qualifyForm" class="space-y-8 relative z-10" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();">
                      
                       <div class="w-full bg-surface-container-highest rounded-full h-2 mb-10 overflow-hidden">
                           <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary h-full transition-all duration-500 ease
